```DAX
% Sales by Product = 
DIVIDE(SUM(supply_chain_data[Revenue generated]),CALCULATE(SUM(supply_chain_data[Revenue generated]), ALL(supply_chain_data))) * 100

Average Defect Rate = 
AVERAGE(supply_chain_data[Defect rates])

Avg. Price = 
AVERAGE(supply_chain_data[Price])

Total Revenue = 
SUM(supply_chain_data[Revenue generated])

Total Shipping Cost = 
sum(supply_chain_data[Shipping costs])

Average Manufacturing Cost = 
AVERAGE(supply_chain_data[Manufacturing costs])

Average Lead Time = 
AVERAGE(supply_chain_data[Lead time])

Total Products Sold = 
SUM(supply_chain_data[Number of products sold])

```
